headline: RBC Capital and TD Cowen Stay Bullish on Block (XYZ)
summary: Block, Inc. (NYSE:XYZ) is one of the 14 Most Promising Fintech Stocks to Invest In. On December 10, RBC Capital analyst Daniel Perlin reaffirmed a Buy rating on Block, Inc. (NYSE:XYZ) with a price target of $90. Earlier, on December 8, TD Cowen maintained its Buy rating on Block, Inc. (NYSE:XYZ) with a $91 price […]
